[[div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:100%;"]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-8592/department.png style="width:100%;" link=#]]
[[div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:100%;"]]
A selfie recieved in an email from D. Partment, the self-proclaimed Chair of SCP-8592.
[[/div]]
